## Tips
1. Use fireworks for celebrations or events.
2. Test different shapes (BALL, STAR, BURST, CREEPER, BALL_LARGE).
3. Combine multiple colors for visual appeal.
4. Use `setPower()` wisely; too high can damage entities.
5. Avoid excessive fireworks in crowded areas to reduce lag.

### Example: Scheduled Firework Show
```java
Bukkit.getScheduler().runTaskTimer(plugin, () -> {
    Firework f = player.getWorld().spawn(player.getLocation(), Firework.class);
    FireworkMeta meta = f.getFireworkMeta();
    meta.addEffect(FireworkEffect.builder().withColor(Color.GREEN).with(FireworkEffect.Type.BALL).build());
    meta.setPower(1);
    f.setFireworkMeta(meta);
}, 0L, 20L); // launch every second
```
